    "media:imagetext": "Breakfast\nFruit yoghurt\n*Fresh fruit appetiser\nMixed grill featuring\nbeef medallion, chicken croquette and beef sausage\naccompanied by sautéed potatoes, grilled tomato\nand mushrooms\nor\nHerb pancake filled with scrambled eggs\nserved with grilled tomato, mushrooms\nand hash-brown potatoes\nBagel and cream cheese\n*Well Being selection\nWe apologise if your choice is not available.\n2014.143012\nRefreshment Bar\nFor your enjoyment\nwe invite you to help yourself\nto a selection of refreshments\navailable between meals.\nComplimentary drinks from the\nbar, tea and coffee are available\nthroughout the flight.\nChampagne is available\nfor purchase.\nDONN D'YOTE WN\n62 WT QB AUG 351Y019-899",
